Southwest U.S. Power Failure Affects Arizona, ABC Station Says

-- B y   A n t h o n y   P a l a z z o
-- 
2011-09-08T23:48:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/southwest-u-s-power-failure-affects-arizona-abc-station-says.html
A  power failure  in the Southwest
U.S. has affected parts of Arizona and  Southern California ,
according to an ABC News affiliate in Phoenix.  San Diego television stations are also reporting blackouts,
the website ABC-15 in Phoenix reported, citing a tweet sent by
Arizona Public Service at around 4:10 p.m. local time.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anthony Palazzo in Los Angeles at 
